Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.65,0:21:00.11,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}白い脆い真実　それだけを留めるの
