Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.54,0:21:15.29,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}遠い声が響く
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:13.98,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\1vc(&H767171&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}脚下的记忆碎片是被浪花拍打上岸
